Dialogue: 5,0:00:05.80,0:00:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Primitive and peculiar,
Dialogue: 5,0:00:07.91,0:00:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,they are unlike any flora or fauna known to us.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:13.91,0:00:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,From time immemorial,
Dialogue: 5,0:00:16.76,0:00:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,men have feared these misshapen entities,
