Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.75,0:01:18.06,Shiver,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,1000)\blur0.6\pos(670,20)}When we were alone
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.78,0:01:22.19,Shiver,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,1000)\blur0.6\pos(30,20)}When we were alone
